==退休之後==
退休後，尼可羅曾在女子棒球隊執教。他的姪子蘭斯（Lance）曾在2003年於巨人隊登上大聯盟。當蘭斯打擊能力下滑時，尼可羅曾教他如何投蝴蝶球。

1997年，他在第五年的票選終於入選名人堂。他也是那年唯一一位入選的球員。<ref name=NDM>{{cite news|title=Phil Niekro enters Hall alone|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1908&dat=19970105&id=1-sfAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0dkEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4860,219472|accessdate=2015-01-17|work={{tsl|en|The Nevada Daily Mail||The Nevada Daily Mail}}|agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]]|date=1997-01-05}}</ref>

2020年12月26日從睡夢中安詳離世，此前與癌魔搏鬥多年，享壽81歲。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Phil Niekro, Hall of Fame Knuckleball Pitcher, Dies at 81|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/27/obituaries/phil-niekro-hall-of-fame-knuckleball-pitcher-dies-at-81.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-12-27|accessdate=2020-12-27|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Richard|last=Goldstein|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309222039/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/27/obituaries/phil-niekro-hall-of-fame-knuckleball-pitcher-dies-at-81.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Hall of Fame knuckleballer Niekro dead at 81|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/phil-niekro-dies-at-81|accessdate=2020-12-27|work=MLB.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227214731/https://www.mlb.com/news/phil-niekro-dies-at-81|dead-url=no}}</ref>

